WEBVTT

01:59.880 --> 02:01.000
These past couple of years,

02:01.080 --> 02:03.000
influencers have been
flocking to Yuanlongli,

02:03.080 --> 02:04.040
especially the 18th floor.

02:04.720 --> 02:08.240
Lots of youngsters
sneak in to shoot videos

02:08.320 --> 02:10.520
or do some urban exploration stuff.

02:14.360 --> 02:18.960
Which means the missing child
came here to film too?

02:22.760 --> 02:23.600
Yes.

02:26.920 --> 02:28.920
So we need to search this place carefully.

02:39.080 --> 02:40.400
Han Zi'ang!

02:42.000 --> 02:43.280
Han Zi'ang!

02:44.280 --> 02:46.160
Your mom wants you home.

02:55.360 --> 02:56.640
Never seen this before?

02:57.960 --> 03:00.080
Look at mine. An upgraded version.

03:04.400 --> 03:06.240
Safer.

03:12.040 --> 03:15.160
Can your upgrade block the sun as well?

03:15.240 --> 03:16.840
Stop hiding.

03:17.800 --> 03:19.280
Your mom wants you back.

03:20.280 --> 03:21.160
Han Zi'ang!

03:35.720 --> 03:36.720
Han Zi'ang.

03:37.440 --> 03:39.240
I see you. Come out.

03:46.640 --> 03:48.960
BY THE ANCIENT IMMORTAL
ALL EVIL IS QUELLED

03:49.560 --> 03:50.480
What's that?

03:50.560 --> 03:52.360
Customized by Yuanlongli.

03:52.880 --> 03:54.200
More effective than police tape.

03:55.480 --> 03:58.960
Say, do you remember this unit?

03:59.040 --> 04:01.840
That case started here.

04:02.440 --> 04:04.240
The black robe. Remember?

04:09.960 --> 04:14.080
Sir, we should focus on
finding that kid first.

04:15.560 --> 04:17.640
Shame. It became a cold case.

04:19.760 --> 04:21.399
Nothing to regret.

04:21.480 --> 04:25.200
And it's not a cold case.
It was mishandled.

04:26.400 --> 04:28.880
Don't talk nonsense.
How was it mishandled?

04:29.920 --> 04:31.120
Did you forget?

04:31.640 --> 04:37.920
That case was the reason I left Weiyang
and transferred to teach in Beijing.

04:41.080 --> 04:42.960
I wasn't cut out to be a detective.

04:43.040 --> 04:45.280
Stop talking like that.
Who says you're not?

04:45.360 --> 04:47.760
If I say you are, then you are.

04:52.960 --> 04:53.840
Sir,

04:54.960 --> 04:57.520
did you bring me here to find the kid?

04:58.160 --> 04:59.000
Or for something else?

05:02.200 --> 05:03.920
What else would it be?

05:04.000 --> 05:07.000
Come on. Let's check this floor.

05:09.320 --> 05:10.480
Han Zi'ang!

05:12.200 --> 05:13.280
Come out!

05:15.080 --> 05:16.080
Han Zi'ang!

05:16.160 --> 05:18.400
BY THE ANCIENT IMMORTAL
ALL EVIL IS QUELLED

05:29.440 --> 05:31.720
-Here he comes.
-He's here.

05:34.520 --> 05:35.360
ROUTE 11
TRAIN STATION TO WORKERS' COMMUNITY

05:35.440 --> 05:36.400
We're here.

05:43.320 --> 05:45.760
-About the same height, right?
-Right.

05:45.840 --> 05:47.800
Put them up where people pass by.

05:47.880 --> 05:50.320
Make them clearly visible. Split up.

05:50.400 --> 05:51.480
Don't waste any of this.

05:51.560 --> 05:53.160
There's a reward if anyone finds him.

05:53.240 --> 05:55.240
-Got it, Officer He.
-Share these among yourselves.

06:01.440 --> 06:04.520
Liangfen for sale! Fresh liangfen!

06:08.400 --> 06:10.000
BE A CIVILIZED NEIGHBOR
AND BUILD A BETTER COMMUNITY

06:20.640 --> 06:21.800
Hand these out.

06:25.280 --> 06:26.200
MISSING PERSONS

06:28.280 --> 06:30.120
YUANLONGLI INTERNATIONAL GARDEN

06:30.200 --> 06:32.840
MISSING PERSONS

06:32.920 --> 06:34.360
The contact numbers are on there.

06:34.440 --> 06:35.360
Call this number.

06:41.440 --> 06:42.440
How about this?

06:42.520 --> 06:43.920
Longhair.

06:44.000 --> 06:45.520
-My goodness!
-Good lord!

06:46.280 --> 06:47.720
-Run quickly!
-Run!

06:47.800 --> 06:50.320
Get back here! Stand still!

06:51.840 --> 06:53.880
Longhair! Get back!

06:59.520 --> 07:00.880
Get back!

07:07.080 --> 07:08.080
Playing big, huh?

07:10.040 --> 07:11.000
Only a quarter of a yuan.

07:11.680 --> 07:12.560
Cut it out.

07:16.960 --> 07:17.960
Take a look at this.

07:18.560 --> 07:19.720
Do you recognize them?

07:21.040 --> 07:22.760
MISSING PERSONS

07:25.880 --> 07:27.640
No. I haven't seen them.

07:28.480 --> 07:31.280
-No.
-We don't know.

07:32.360 --> 07:33.560
Alright.

07:34.360 --> 07:36.600
In that case, keep an eye out.

07:36.680 --> 07:37.800
Sure.

07:37.880 --> 07:38.960
Answer!

07:39.040 --> 07:40.920
Of course.

07:44.000 --> 07:46.880
We'll take care of it.
Don't worry, Officer He.

07:48.760 --> 07:49.920
Careful.

07:54.760 --> 07:56.480
Smile.

07:57.280 --> 07:58.960
-Make it quick.
-No problem.

08:00.040 --> 08:01.600
Please drive safely, Officer He.

08:04.320 --> 08:05.520
Take care.

08:09.280 --> 08:10.720
KIOSK

08:15.160 --> 08:18.440
Page this number. 1276165888.

08:18.520 --> 08:20.680
"Mr. Jin. Urgent. Call me back
as soon as possible."

08:23.160 --> 08:25.440
"Urgent. Call me back
as soon as possible."

08:25.520 --> 08:26.760
LIKE GENERAL STORE

08:26.840 --> 08:28.520
Hong Kong, China, has been handed back.

08:28.600 --> 08:29.440
BUSINESS TRANSFORMATION

08:29.520 --> 08:32.120
We need to keep up with the times.

08:32.640 --> 08:36.679
From now on, everything
runs on a business line.

08:36.760 --> 08:39.799
What are our core businesses?

08:41.360 --> 08:43.960
-You tell me.
-They are loansharking,

08:44.039 --> 08:46.920
debt collection, hair salons,
and protection fees.

08:49.080 --> 08:50.200
Get lost.

08:50.840 --> 08:53.480
You trained all day,
and that's what you learned?

08:53.560 --> 08:56.440
That's called public management.

08:56.520 --> 08:58.400
Public management!

08:58.480 --> 08:59.840
Loansharking?

08:59.920 --> 09:01.960
Mr. Jin.

09:02.040 --> 09:04.040
Why didn't you return the page?

09:04.120 --> 09:05.560
Something has happened.

09:05.640 --> 09:08.120
MAY WEALTH FLOW YOUR WAY

09:08.200 --> 09:10.160
MISSING PERSONS

09:10.240 --> 09:12.720
Manlang was in Yuanlongli yesterday?

09:12.800 --> 09:17.120
Yeah. Wolf told me himself last night.

09:17.840 --> 09:21.000
I saw two bloodstained clothes in his bag.

09:24.320 --> 09:26.800
-No wonder he skipped training.
-Tell me about it.

09:28.720 --> 09:30.320
-Wolf is here.
-That rascal!

09:32.120 --> 09:33.720
Mr. Jin.

09:33.800 --> 09:34.960
Please…

09:35.040 --> 09:36.760
Where have you been?

10:01.920 --> 10:04.480
Officer He. No one has seen her.

10:09.680 --> 10:11.400
You can teleport now?

10:11.920 --> 10:13.400
You were at the snack street just now,

10:13.480 --> 10:15.280
and now you're at Jinsha Market.

10:15.360 --> 10:17.280
-Came to tip him off?
-Officer He,

10:18.040 --> 10:19.720
he's here for training.

10:20.240 --> 10:21.440
We've restructured.

10:22.120 --> 10:24.400
We don't break the law anymore.

10:25.320 --> 10:28.520
Jin Manshan, do you believe that yourself?

10:29.280 --> 10:30.680
If you don't believe me, ask them.

10:31.760 --> 10:35.280
What are our four main sectors?

10:35.360 --> 10:39.120
-Public management.
-Public management.

10:39.200 --> 10:42.400
-High-risk finance.
-High-risk finance.

10:42.480 --> 10:46.000
-Security services.
-Security services.

10:46.080 --> 10:50.720
-Beauty and wellness.
-Beauty and wellness.

11:05.800 --> 11:06.840
Fine.

11:07.880 --> 11:10.000
Since you've got people here,
I'll leave this with you.

11:10.080 --> 11:11.400
-Ask around for me.
-No problem.

11:15.680 --> 11:16.520
Where's your brother?

11:17.760 --> 11:18.840
Jin Manlang?

11:20.640 --> 11:21.920
He went to buy training materials.

11:43.520 --> 11:45.920
LOUNGE

11:56.720 --> 11:59.320
REMITTANCE NOTICE, AMOUNT: 12,000 YUAN

12:31.920 --> 12:35.840
FOR DRAMATIC EFFECT. DO NOT IMITATE

13:37.920 --> 13:40.000
Yuanlongli

13:40.080 --> 13:42.240
Eighteenth floor

13:42.320 --> 13:45.960
Eighteenth floor with 18 pillars

13:46.040 --> 13:50.200
Eighteen bodies, 18 heads

13:51.200 --> 13:54.640
Kids, who taught you that rhyme?

13:56.120 --> 13:59.080
Whoever tells me gets chocolate.

13:59.160 --> 14:01.080
-A classmate!
-An old man!

14:01.160 --> 14:03.480
One at a time, please.
Who taught you that?

14:09.720 --> 14:14.240
Officer, are you here about
the two people who went missing upstairs?

14:18.600 --> 14:20.160
I'm really sorry.

14:20.680 --> 14:22.560
Should I take you to the hospital?

14:22.640 --> 14:24.000
It's fine. No need.

14:24.080 --> 14:25.080
We're here.

14:37.360 --> 14:39.560
Maybe you can come in and wash up.

14:42.800 --> 14:44.240
I've got slippers.

15:07.440 --> 15:09.760
This towel is new. Never used.

15:10.720 --> 15:13.480
The bathroom is right behind you.

15:14.840 --> 15:16.040
Thank you.

15:20.960 --> 15:22.040
Wait…

16:00.600 --> 16:02.560
-Thank you.
-It's nothing.

16:24.280 --> 16:25.640
I have some gauze here.

16:25.720 --> 16:27.480
Want me to help?

16:30.280 --> 16:31.760
Oh… Sure.

16:44.760 --> 16:45.800
Hold still.

16:59.160 --> 17:00.280
You can keep the slippers.

17:10.520 --> 17:13.480
By the way, I'm Ran Fangxu.

17:14.640 --> 17:16.000
I'm Qiao Suqing.

17:40.960 --> 17:42.440
MISSING PERSONS

17:56.520 --> 17:57.680
Sorry about that.

18:23.760 --> 18:25.200
You little brat.

18:25.280 --> 18:27.480
You're talking nonsense again.
Watch your mouth.

18:27.560 --> 18:29.960
Silly boy! All that
for a piece of chocolate?

18:31.320 --> 18:32.200
Don't hit him.

18:33.080 --> 18:34.320
What's going on?

18:34.400 --> 18:36.080
Why did you teach him that rhyme?

18:36.160 --> 18:37.720
I didn't want to.

18:42.280 --> 18:44.480
This morning, I picked up
a flyer by the roadside.

18:44.560 --> 18:46.120
That rhyme was printed on it.

18:46.200 --> 18:48.080
It said if you don't pass it on,
there'll be bloodshed.

18:48.160 --> 18:49.320
That's nonsense.

18:49.400 --> 18:50.840
It's real.

18:50.920 --> 18:52.280
I'm not making it up.

18:52.800 --> 18:54.520
This morning, right when
I opened the door,

18:54.600 --> 18:56.080
something bad happened.

18:56.600 --> 18:58.240
There was someone…

19:06.200 --> 19:07.200
Someone?

19:07.280 --> 19:09.320
No one. I remembered it wrong.

19:11.720 --> 19:14.040
Don't be scared.
I'm in charge around here.

19:14.120 --> 19:17.000
Stop asking. I can't remember.

19:20.680 --> 19:22.240
HE

19:22.880 --> 19:25.640
Ma'am, if anything
comes back to you, page me.

19:25.720 --> 19:26.680
Okay.

19:40.080 --> 19:41.240
Officer,

19:41.760 --> 19:43.520
I recognize that person.

19:43.600 --> 19:45.960
He had a bag too.
There was a lot of blood inside.

19:48.280 --> 19:49.800
Who was it? Tell me.

19:49.880 --> 19:52.240
Then I want another chocolate.

20:19.520 --> 20:20.800
Rooftop?

21:04.320 --> 21:06.000
PATTIA CLUB, THAI MASSAGE

21:27.000 --> 21:29.040
FIRE EXTINGUISHER

22:18.880 --> 22:23.000
YUXI CIGARETTE

22:23.080 --> 22:24.680
Flip-top Yuxi cigarettes.

22:25.280 --> 22:28.000
Mainly for bosses.
Twenty yuan for one packet.

22:43.080 --> 22:44.800
FIRE EXTINGUISHER

23:11.200 --> 23:15.640
01: I HAVE KEY INFORMATION
ABOUT THE YUANLONGLI CASE

23:34.560 --> 23:36.080
Hello, 126?

23:37.080 --> 23:38.680
Please page this number again.

23:38.760 --> 23:41.200
8233585.

23:42.440 --> 23:43.760
Page it ten times.

23:44.280 --> 23:45.320
Leave a message.

23:45.960 --> 23:49.520
"I have key information
about the Yuanlongli case.

23:50.280 --> 23:54.200
Come to Number 407, New York Block.

23:54.280 --> 23:55.400
As soon as possible."

23:57.240 --> 23:59.080
Please page it ten times.

24:00.160 --> 24:01.040
Thanks.

24:25.280 --> 24:27.800
01: I HAVE KEY INFORMATION
ABOUT THE YUANLONGLI CASE

24:56.280 --> 24:57.440
Are you okay?

25:07.040 --> 25:08.320
RAN FANGXU'S ID

25:10.440 --> 25:11.760
Don't be nervous.

25:11.840 --> 25:12.680
If you're hurt,

25:12.760 --> 25:14.840
come find me at the criminal department
of the Nanshan Branch.

25:14.920 --> 25:16.200
The name is Ran Fangxu.

25:19.800 --> 25:20.840
I'm really sorry.

25:24.960 --> 25:26.120
Qiao.

25:26.200 --> 25:28.000
Can I borrow your phone?

25:35.200 --> 25:37.440
There's a group fight
at Qingsong Cement Factory.

25:37.520 --> 25:39.360
The whole squad's gone. No one left.

25:40.400 --> 25:41.480
Oh, right.

25:41.560 --> 25:43.240
He Yuanhang should be free.

25:43.320 --> 25:44.840
You can try calling him.

25:45.360 --> 25:46.640
Alright.

25:54.680 --> 25:57.840
The top two floors were rented
by a big boss a couple of years ago.

25:57.920 --> 26:00.360
He secretly turned
the 18th floor into a club.

26:01.600 --> 26:05.000
Half of the 17th floor was staff dorms.

26:05.080 --> 26:07.480
The other half was rented out.

26:08.080 --> 26:09.400
Earlier this year, there was
a nationwide crackdown on prostitution.

26:10.000 --> 26:12.120
Someone reported the 18th floor,

26:12.200 --> 26:13.480
and it's been shut since.

26:14.080 --> 26:15.520
Then what's with this door?

26:15.600 --> 26:18.800
Before, drunk customers used
to climb out to the rooftop from here.

26:18.880 --> 26:21.240
We were worried about accidents,
so we made it a hidden door.

26:21.320 --> 26:22.520
Why didn't you mention this yesterday?

26:22.600 --> 26:24.680
Those two couldn't have had a key.

26:25.200 --> 26:26.240
It's open.

26:58.480 --> 26:59.920
Officer Ran,

27:00.000 --> 27:03.160
please don't tell anyone
I brought you to the rooftop.

27:03.240 --> 27:05.200
Up there is Mr. Ge's territory.

27:05.280 --> 27:06.720
I can't afford to cross him.

27:06.800 --> 27:08.560
Does Mr. Ge have a key?

27:08.640 --> 27:09.800
Let me tell you.

27:09.880 --> 27:12.640
That old man is Manager Qian's uncle.

27:12.720 --> 27:16.040
But don't worry. The Qian family
is shrewd and tightfisted.

27:16.640 --> 27:17.960
He wouldn't lend out the key.

27:19.040 --> 27:20.240
Alright.

27:31.760 --> 27:32.960
BEIJING TRAVEL

27:54.960 --> 27:57.280
YUXI

28:08.680 --> 28:11.040
RETRIBUTION FOR STEALING CHICKENS

28:23.480 --> 28:25.280
PUBLIC SECURITY

28:26.160 --> 28:28.360
Move it. We've got a homicide.

28:28.440 --> 28:29.360
Stay sharp.

28:30.280 --> 28:31.960
We've searched the 18th floor.

28:32.040 --> 28:33.760
What could we have missed?

28:33.840 --> 28:35.800
Officer Ran is a top graduate of PPSUC.

28:35.880 --> 28:37.840
If he says there's a lead,
there is one for sure.

29:13.080 --> 29:14.440
Something big's going down.

29:15.040 --> 29:16.920
This is where Mr. Ge keeps chickens.

29:17.000 --> 29:18.000
Where are the chickens?

29:18.080 --> 29:20.720
That's exactly the problem.

29:22.440 --> 29:23.400
There's something here.

29:25.960 --> 29:27.680
Officer Qu, over here.

29:31.920 --> 29:33.400
You little rascal.

29:34.320 --> 29:36.520
-I'll beat you to death!
-Don't come closer. I'm a police officer!

29:48.520 --> 29:50.280
Doubao, come in.

29:50.360 --> 29:52.840
What took you so long?

29:52.920 --> 29:56.360
Let go. Let go of my hand.

29:56.440 --> 29:57.640
Come in, Doubao.

29:57.720 --> 29:59.160
Why would I go in?

29:59.240 --> 30:01.600
-Let go.
-I won't!

30:01.680 --> 30:02.560
Get in here.

30:02.640 --> 30:04.120
You killed my chickens!

30:04.200 --> 30:06.400
That's assaulting an officer.
I'm warning you.

30:09.040 --> 30:10.120
Stop!

30:10.760 --> 30:11.920
What took you so long?

30:12.000 --> 30:13.760
I paged you over a dozen times.

30:14.840 --> 30:16.560
Come with me. I'll tell you.

30:23.520 --> 30:24.520
Are you

30:25.040 --> 30:28.080
8233585?

30:28.840 --> 30:30.440
I came to see you.

30:31.160 --> 30:32.880
Good.

30:32.960 --> 30:33.960
I'll be straight with you.

30:34.040 --> 30:37.520
I don't have much to go on.
I only saw it once.

30:37.600 --> 30:38.760
You saw it?

30:38.840 --> 30:40.320
Yeah. I did.

30:40.400 --> 30:41.520
Clear as day.

30:41.600 --> 30:43.160
I saw you too.

30:43.240 --> 30:44.600
Get down!

30:44.680 --> 30:46.640
Get down! Get down now!

30:46.720 --> 30:50.440
Once it's cooked,
it goes straight to the table.

30:54.360 --> 30:55.200
Old man,

30:56.240 --> 30:57.520
I'm here…

30:59.880 --> 31:01.480
Open the door! I'm He Yuanhang.

31:09.000 --> 31:12.160
Sir, I'm here to check the gas.

31:12.240 --> 31:12.920
WEIYANG GAS

31:13.000 --> 31:15.600
Gas inspection? It's inside.

31:15.680 --> 31:16.880
Go check it yourself.

31:20.080 --> 31:22.240
Officer He, you were looking for me?

31:22.320 --> 31:23.600
You paged me, didn't you?

31:24.200 --> 31:26.480
I paged the number
on the missing persons notice.

31:26.560 --> 31:27.920
That's my number.

31:28.000 --> 31:29.320
Who were you talking to just now?

31:29.400 --> 31:31.000
Someone from the gas company.

31:31.080 --> 31:32.280
Gas company?

31:40.000 --> 31:42.520
Officer He! It's me! It's me!

31:43.480 --> 31:44.320
Jin Manlang?

31:46.120 --> 31:47.520
Punk.

31:49.520 --> 31:51.360
Are you here to silence them?

31:51.440 --> 31:52.560
I'm innocent.

31:52.640 --> 31:53.880
I didn't kill anyone.

31:53.960 --> 31:55.160
I didn't mean to cover anything up.

31:55.240 --> 31:56.680
How did you know
I was going to ask about a murder?

32:03.280 --> 32:04.120
Rascal.

32:04.200 --> 32:05.520
You screwed this up.

32:10.080 --> 32:12.720
All 18 chickens had their throats slit,

32:12.800 --> 32:15.360
and now you're turning it around,
saying I'm the killer?

32:15.960 --> 32:16.920
Put that down!

32:20.840 --> 32:22.680
Where are the chickens?

32:22.760 --> 32:24.200
Eighteen victims.

32:24.280 --> 32:25.560
All dumped on the rooftop.

32:25.640 --> 32:27.560
You think I could just
stand by and do nothing?

32:36.440 --> 32:37.720
What are you waiting for?

32:37.800 --> 32:39.840
-Secure the evidence now.
-Alright. Move.

32:40.720 --> 32:41.720
Fangxu.

32:43.520 --> 32:44.360
Next time something like this happens,

32:44.440 --> 32:46.520
shouldn't you call in
the criminal department?

32:47.120 --> 32:48.400
-I…
-I'm not blaming you.

32:49.080 --> 32:51.320
It's fine if I made a wasted trip.

32:51.840 --> 32:53.840
I'm just concerned about how others feel.

32:53.920 --> 32:56.480
After all, everyone showed up
because of you, Officer Ran.

32:56.560 --> 32:57.400
Right?

33:05.240 --> 33:06.720
Sorry about that, Officer Qu.

33:06.800 --> 33:08.440
I caused you trouble.

33:09.120 --> 33:12.720
But these bloodstains
were likely a smokescreen.

33:12.800 --> 33:15.720
It's possible the killer used
chicken blood to cover up human blood.

33:19.600 --> 33:21.520
Officer Qu, we're done.

33:23.040 --> 33:24.520
Alright. Wrap it up.

33:24.600 --> 33:26.480
Take him back for a statement.

33:39.520 --> 33:42.120
Officer Ran, let's go.

33:43.800 --> 33:46.080
You go ahead. I'll collect some samples.

34:02.800 --> 34:05.120
Officer He. Take it easy.

34:05.200 --> 34:06.280
Easy?

34:06.880 --> 34:08.000
I'm innocent, really.

34:08.080 --> 34:09.400
Get in the car.

34:09.480 --> 34:11.080
Eighteen chickens, you know?

34:11.639 --> 34:13.760
I handpicked each of them
and raised them myself.

34:13.840 --> 34:15.320
Don't try anything silly.

34:15.400 --> 34:17.120
Now they're dead for no reason.

34:17.719 --> 34:18.800
You guys get in first.

34:18.880 --> 34:20.679
You'd better get to the bottom of this.

34:21.280 --> 34:24.159
Otherwise, I'm staying
at the station and not leaving.

34:24.239 --> 34:25.159
Get in.

34:27.920 --> 34:30.920
Qu, this case is perfect for you.

34:31.520 --> 34:35.000
Make sure you dig into it properly
and give Mr. Ge a satisfactory answer.

34:36.000 --> 34:37.639
This case suits you too.

34:37.719 --> 34:39.679
He's in handcuffs? Must be serious.

34:41.040 --> 34:42.280
Looks like your temporary transfer
is getting extended.

34:43.520 --> 34:44.800
Will you even make it back?

34:45.920 --> 34:48.320
Well. You're just jealous.

34:48.400 --> 34:49.639
I'm good at what I do.

34:49.719 --> 34:51.400
I can crack any case in a day,
however tough it is.

34:52.880 --> 34:53.920
Han.

34:54.000 --> 34:54.840
Shouhu.

34:54.920 --> 34:57.440
Clear out my desk in six days.

34:57.520 --> 34:59.720
I'll be back on time,
just like Hong Kong, China.

35:00.440 --> 35:02.320
"Good at what I do"? Even
your own apprentice doesn't trust you.

35:03.280 --> 35:05.680
He called me when something happened.

35:13.200 --> 35:18.920
POLICE BY THE PEOPLE
FOR THE PEOPLE

35:21.400 --> 35:22.480
FORENSIC EVIDENCE INTAKE

35:22.560 --> 35:23.400
Sign here.

35:23.480 --> 35:26.920
FORENSIC DEPARTMENT EVIDENCE
TRANSFER FORM, SUBMITTED BY HE YUANHANG

35:36.800 --> 35:38.800
SUBMITTED BY RAN FANGXU

35:40.600 --> 35:42.720
Run the tests as soon as possible.
I'll treat you to a meal later.

35:46.960 --> 35:50.280
I told you. If you dress so elegantly,
you won't catch criminals.

35:56.960 --> 36:00.000
Why are you still standing there?
The suspect's been arrested.

36:00.080 --> 36:01.520
FORENSIC DEPARTMENT

36:05.520 --> 36:06.680
NOTEBOOK

36:06.760 --> 36:10.440
FORENSIC DEPARTMENT
INTERROGATION ROOM

36:11.920 --> 36:17.120
LENIENCY FOR CONFESSION
SEVERITY FOR RESISTANCE

36:17.200 --> 36:20.600
Wolfie, we've known
each other a long time.

36:20.680 --> 36:22.840
I won't need to repeat the rules, right?

36:22.920 --> 36:24.560
No.

36:28.440 --> 36:29.520
Take a look at this.

36:30.120 --> 36:31.120
Start from the beginning.

36:31.200 --> 36:33.120
Who are these two? Where did they go?

36:37.960 --> 36:39.160
MISSING PERSONS

36:43.680 --> 36:47.680
Officer, if you're asking me,
who am I supposed to ask?

36:47.760 --> 36:49.160
I honestly don't know.

36:51.640 --> 36:53.800
Alright. That's enough.

36:56.640 --> 36:57.800
Wrap it up and leave.

36:58.720 --> 37:01.480
Officer He, what are you doing?

37:01.560 --> 37:03.360
Don't be mad.

37:03.440 --> 37:05.960
I'll talk. I'll talk, alright?

37:57.680 --> 38:00.640
Ten thousand in cash upfront.
Another 30,000 after it's done.

38:01.280 --> 38:03.880
The cigarettes are a little extra for you.

38:07.120 --> 38:09.000
You want them laid out or tied up?

38:09.840 --> 38:11.320
I want them gone.
